nodes.text: Overlord Rrynt'vor was the overseer of the Rak'qua, a group of Nautolan warriors that had taken control of Station Gamma during the time of the Galactic Civil War. He led his men from his base deep down in the asteroid station.
In a nearby cave, Rrynt'vor kept his pet, a giant creature named Ageaughu.

Rrynt'vor appeared as a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
